<p>“It’s a very complex path to navigate," warns Dzhengozov. "Finance chiefs must scrutinise contracts, subscriptions and expense policies to mitigate the risks. Focusing on cross-functional collaboration can help to get messaging right and preserve customer trust.”</p><div class="fadeArticle"></div></div><script nodelay>
